overview:
TravelBid.com.my is Malaysia’s 1st Reverse Auction website to fully specialize in Travel & Lifestyle Products. It is created for today’s online savvy and contemporary pop-culture audience, highly appreciative of innovative travel shopping, and buying it in style!

The Team behind TravelBid has over 20 years of cumulative experience in the Travel Trade. Rest assured we are here to serve you only the coolest, Top-Notch & stunning leisure shopping experience at unbelievably low prices - all from the comfort of your home!

Member able to bid the travel packages that we offer with the lowest unique bid. Besides bidding, we are allowing our Member to buy the travel packages that we are having as well. Feel free to visit our website www.TravelBid.com.my to find out more information about us.
